{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had no experience in these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it all of a sudden dawns on me that he wants me to take care of this money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I kind of walked over to him and grabbed the money, and tucked it into my-- into my belt, because my pockets weren't big enough to take this wad of money.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I understood I didn't want it to show.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyhow, we-- everybody-- my Uncle Bob happened to be one flight up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I still could see him coming, sneaking, hand-over-hand, very carefully down one flight of stair, and running down the little hallway, and fleeing out the double stairs, out of the hiding place, and disappearing into the night.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was not picked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my grandfa-- my grandmother, my aunt, my cousin, my father, my mother, my sister, and myself-- we were taken into the truck and brought to the theater-- the Dutch-- or the Jewish theater, as it was called-- the [INAUDIBLE] where everybody was being held until they would put them into cattle cars and bring them to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was put into a building, because I was a young child, which was called the creche.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why they called it the creche, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't think anybody has ever figured that out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was called the creche, spelled C-R-E-C-H-E.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in this children holding area, I came in-- in the middle of the night, because it took quite a while before we finally were, literally, processed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I get there somewhere around about midnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We get into this-- I get in this big room, and somebody walks up to me and says, yeah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Go and take that bunk.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
